lead_paragraph: Tommy Armstrong Jr. isn't pouting over not being voted a team captain, even though he is going into his fourth year as Nebraska's starting quarterback and was a captain in 2015.

headline.print_headline: Huskers' Armstrong Says Captain's Title Not Needed to Lead
